 2ï¸âƒ£ Static vs Dynamic Website

 ğŸ”¹ Static Website

 Sirf HTML, CSS, JS
 Content fixed hota hai
 Fast & low cost
 Server logic nahi hota

Example:
Portfolio website, simple business website

---

 ğŸ”¹ Dynamic Website

 Frontend + Backend + Database
 Content user ke according change hota hai
 Login, forms, dashboard possible

Example:
E-commerce website, social media, banking portals

