 7ï¸âƒ£ AWS S3 Static Website Hosting (Hands-On)

 ğŸ”¹ What You Did:

Tumne apni static website ko AWS S3 bucket ke through live host kiya.

 ğŸ”¹ Process (Conceptual Steps):

